### Critical checks for WCAG 1.4.8 & 1.4.10:
- ✅ **Text ≤ 80 characters per line** (e.g., 12–14pt at 1.5 line-height)
- ✅ **Line spacing ≥ 1.5x**
- ✅ **No horizontal scrolling** when zoomed to 400%
